description: The hungry people on the streets of Seattle are getting a taste of many kinds of cuisines, all thanks to Kabob ‘n Kabob. The crew at this cart is fusing foods from Afghanistan, Pakistan, India, and the Mediterranean, to grill up an eclectic selection of delicious kabobs that all make for the perfect grub on the go. Come on by Kabob ‘n Kabob (or have the cart come cater your next event) for the best flavors that the world has to offer!
name: Kabob 'n Kabob
